{
  "stem": "12491.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We put up the machine gun on the, on the roof of the camp, and we put out three guys with rifles on each side of the road.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We stopped them all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We took off their uniforms, took away, took away their weapons, and send them to the Americans in their underwear by the hundreds.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The weapons we stored in a room, in one of the factory rooms.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we took hundreds upon hundreds of very small weapons.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were not carrying any bigger weapons.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Unfortunately, some-- there was a situation where a group of soldiers on horses were galloping from east to west.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And people who-- other people in the camp told that they probably are the Russians.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they started running towards them to greet them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But these were Germans, and they started shooting and killed a few of us-- of our people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The Germans most likely got scared, because it was already after the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And theoretically, they were not supposed to have any weapons anymore, by the, by the rules of the capitulation.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But unfortunately, this happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We also lost a few people who ate food which was left by Schindler in his warehouse, consisting of very fat pork in cans.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they ate it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They died.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They couldn't-- their stomachs couldn't take it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "After all these years of starvation, they could not take this kind of food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We had a guard at the warehouse, because whoever was in charge of our group must have been smart enough to realize that this can happen.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But somehow, they managed to get the cans of the-- canned fat pork.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And unfortunately, a few of them died.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, he left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were in charge of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
